	("zh_Hans_CN",  "LOC_PEDIA_CONCEPTS_PAGE_HD_CITY_PAGE_CHAPTER_HD_AMENITY_PARA_1",                           "城市免费宜居度改回1点。并增加了一档新的宜居状态："),
	("zh_Hans_CN",  "LOC_PEDIA_CONCEPTS_PAGE_HD_CITY_PAGE_CHAPTER_HD_AMENITY_PARA_2",                           "
